Invocation Name: restaurant club
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Restaurant club is a unique way to help locals connect to their favorite restaurants. It is a such easy way using the power of voice.
When you want to reach out to example restaurant, SAY : Alexa ask restaurant club to open green house , then green house will ask you what would you like to do?
If you need a menu SAY: send me the menu. 
If you want to get something form the menu just SAY : I would like to get ... whatever.
